WEBVTT

00:02.085 --> 00:05.622
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:07.924 --> 00:08.925
Hey, Mr. Clavin's back.

00:09.426 --> 00:10.427
Whatta you say, Woody?

00:10.427 --> 00:11.928
How was your trip to Expo?

00:11.928 --> 00:13.430
Oh, a once-in-a-lifetime
experience.

00:13.430 --> 00:14.431
I tell ya.

00:14.431 --> 00:15.932
You know, no ears have heard,

00:15.932 --> 00:17.934
no eyes have seen the
wonders I've experienced

00:17.934 --> 00:19.436
these past two weeks in Canada.

00:19.436 --> 00:22.439
If I died right now,
I'd be a happy person.

00:22.439 --> 00:24.941
You wouldn't be the only one.

00:24.941 --> 00:27.444
Hey, uh, Normie, you should have seen

00:27.444 --> 00:29.946
this 3-D movie they had
about life in Vancouver.

00:29.946 --> 00:31.448
You know, with those glasses on,

00:31.448 --> 00:33.316
you felt like you were really there.

00:33.316 --> 00:36.653
You were there, Cliff.

00:36.653 --> 00:37.654
I've been readin' up on Expo.

00:37.654 --> 00:39.155
Did you catch that bullet
train they got there?

00:39.155 --> 00:40.657
No, I guess I missed that one.

00:40.657 --> 00:43.159
Did you see the Great Hall of Ramses?

00:43.159 --> 00:47.163
Uh, no, no, I guess that
slid right by me... yeah.

00:47.163 --> 00:48.665
Uh, how about the U.S. space exhibit?

00:48.665 --> 00:52.052
No.

00:52.052 --> 00:53.553
Chinese acrobats?

00:53.553 --> 00:54.554
Uh-uh.

00:54.554 --> 00:57.807
SAM: Hey, Cliff! How was Expo?

00:57.807 --> 01:00.643
A major disappointment, Sam.

01:03.563 --> 01:07.100
(piano plays)

01:07.100 --> 01:09.569
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:09.569 --> 01:12.572
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:12.572 --> 01:15.575
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:15.575 --> 01:19.079
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:19.079 --> 01:23.950
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:23.950 --> 01:26.786
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:26.786 --> 01:32.292
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:32.292 --> 01:36.796
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:36.796 --> 01:39.299
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:39.299 --> 01:41.801
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:41.801 --> 01:47.307
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

01:47.307 --> 01:49.809
? You want to go where people know ?

01:49.809 --> 01:52.312
? People are all the same ?

